metalign.parsing

Class MidiEventParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • metalign.parsing.MidiEventParser
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EventParser

    public class MidiEventParser
extends java.lang.Object
implements EventParser
    A MidiEventParser handles the interfacing between this program and MIDI files. It can read in MIDI events from a file with run().

    One EventParser is required per song you wish to parse.

    Author:
    Andrew McLeod - 23 October, 2014
